# On Your Own Preference

When the user says **"on your own"**, treat it as a strict execution mode.

## Required behavior

- Perform the requested work end-to-end without asking follow-up questions.
- Run needed commands, apply changes, and verify outcomes proactively.
- Do not interrupt with status pings unless blocked by a hard external constraint.
- Share only concise completion results and relevant verification.
- Ask questions only when absolutely blocked (missing credentials, unavailable service, or ambiguous destructive action).

